external_knowledge:
1 kiloparsec (kpc) equals 1,000 parsecs, a unit of distance where 1 parsec equals approximately 3.26 light-years; 
Astronomical objects are often categorized based on their properties and observation conditions; 
The distance of an astronomical object is a fundamental property in understanding its behavior and characteristics.

sql:
SELECT object_type, AVG(luminosity) AS average_luminosity
FROM astronomical_objects
GROUP BY object_type;
